text: Wayne's World is a 1992 American comedy movie from Paramount Pictures, starring Mike Myers and Dana Carvey. It is based on a segment of the same name from television's Saturday Night Live. It made more money than any other movie based on a SNL segment. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1992 movies Category:1992 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Cult movies Category:Movies based on TV series Category:Movies set in Illinois Category:Self-reflexive movies Category:Screenplays by Mike Myers Category:Multilingual movies Category:Movies directed by Penelope Spheeris Category:Fictional television shows
